text: Joanne Nicole Rodríguez Hacohen (born 14 August 1997) is a Guatemalan track cyclist. She competed at the 2014 Summer Youth Olympics, 2019 Pan American Games, and 2021 UCI Track Cycling World Championships. She holds the Guatemalan records in track cycling in the flying 200 metres time trial. == References == Category:1997 births Category:Cyclists Category:Guatemalan people Category:Living people
